{{Quote|They were a great favorite of Zan Yant's. The music was written to celebrate the Shoosha family's escape from Brentaal. Had that battle not taken place, the Variations might never have existed.|Barriss Offee|<ref name="MedStar II">''[[MedStar II: Jedi Healer]]''</ref>}}
The "'''Vissëncant Variations'''" was the name given to a popular [[Classical music|classical]] piece<ref name="MedStar II" /> consisting of fifteen variations,<ref name="MedStar I">''[[MedStar I: Battle Surgeons]]''</ref> composed by famed [[Musician/Legends|musician]] [[Bann Shoosha]] to celebrate the Shoosha family's escape from [[Brentaal IV/Legends|Brentaal]]. It was the favorite musical composition of [[Zabrak/Legends|Zabrak]] musician and surgeon [[Zan Yant]].<ref name="MedStar II" />

